  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.2.1">
<l>ūṉvā ṭavuṇṇā tuyirkā valiṭṭē yuṭaliṟ piriyāp pulaṉain tunontu</l>
<l>tāmvā ṭavāṭat tavamcey yavēṇṭā tamatā vimaiyō rulakā ḷakiṟpīr</l>
<l>kāṉā ṭamaññaik kaṇamā ṭamāṭē kayalā ṭukāṉīrp paḻaṉam puṭaipōy</l>
<l>tēṉā ṭamāṭak koṭiyā ṭutillait tiruccit rakūṭam ceṉṟucēr miṉkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who would rule the world of celestials as your own,</l>
<l rend="indent">not eating so the flesh withers, giving protection to your life,</l>
<l>Do not do penance so that your five senses, inseparable from your body,</l>
<l rend="indent">continually waste away!</l>
<l>Go and gather at Tiruccitrakūṭam in Tillai</l>
<l rend="indent">where creepers on houses sway, as bees flit going to [all] sides of the fields</l>
<l>With water in [their] channels where fish frolic nearby,</l>
<l rend="indent">as flocks of peacocks dance while the groves sway.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
